@startuml
title "UC-07: Prepare Orders Kitchen"

actor Cook
participant "Mr. Daebak System" as System

== Load Cook Orders ==
Cook -> System: 1. Request assigned orders
activate System
System --> Cook: 2. Order list\n(RECEIVED/PREPARING status)
deactivate System

== Start Cooking ==
Cook -> System: 3. Update order status\n(order_id, status: PREPARING)
activate System
System --> Cook: 4. Status updated successfully
deactivate System

== Complete Cooking ==
Cook -> System: 5. Update order status\n(order_id, status: DELIVERING)
activate System
System --> Cook: 6. Status updated successfully
deactivate System

@enduml
